{"tid":1038386,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貪玩男打警方電話千四次","createTime":"2019-02-26T15:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T20:31:08.000Z","uid":30788,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5ee8b661e45a2237ccd0e6d3443c154eebba75fe","tid":1038386,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】無業漢聲稱為了解悶，竟於九日間致電999報案中心及各區警署報案室逾一千四百次，其間更無聊地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將兩部已分別接通報案中心及警署的手機併攏，讓兩方的警員「講電話」。他</span></span>昨在屯門裁判法院承認一項不斷打電話罪，還柙至本月十七日判刑。 廿五歲被告張浩鋒被控於去年十月八日至十六日間，向新界總區指揮及控制中心（即999報案中心）撥出六百零四個滋擾電話。 案情指被告以失效電話卡致電999報案中心，其中一百九十九次有報案中心職員聽到耳筒傳來警署報案室同袍的聲音，其餘則是無聲電話。警方拘捕被告後在其一部有登記號碼的手機，發現他於九日內致電各區警署報案室達八百一十次，另搜出三張紀錄不同警署部門的電話號碼紙。 警誡下他承認因太悶而犯案，自覺這樣做好玩，有時他無法自控地不斷打電話。 案件編號：TMCC4056/14"},{"pid":"767039cd54f9440f32cb79183dd651330b248118","tid":1038386,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87500bebcb48531d996838eeb035a72672196a6","tid":1038386,"uid":220701,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150204/19028897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150204%2F19028897&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6ST1kznsNOvA2%2BdQC7BC3ts%3D&h=8a7da0dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150204%2F19028897&h=40304a19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150204/19028897</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2015 dnlm"},{"pid":"446192765c5111a7820e890311c4cc0092a2c5b4","tid":1038386,"uid":144784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8313